Vulcan Mobile bundles and queries third-party data sources. Attribution and
licensing for those sources is recorded here.

---

OBDb Community Database (https://github.com/OBDb)

The standard SAE J1979 PID definitions in server/pidStandard.json and the
vehicle-specific PID definitions cached in server/pidCache.json are sourced
from the OBDb open-source project. The data is normalized at integration
time but retains the same semantic content (signal definitions, value
ranges, decode metadata) as the upstream source.

